      pose proof (BProv_Ax_s_dvdTermTermAt_mul_right D
        (tSucc (tVar 0)) multiple1 (tSucc bound1) hdvd) as hmul.
      replace consequent
        with (dvdTermTermAt (tSucc (tVar 0))
